quote:
This is a repeat after me rap!

All around the country coast to coast, People always ask me what I like most,

I don't wanna brag, I don't wanna boast

I always tell 'em I like toast.

Make TOAST yeah TOAST

Now there's no secret to toast perfection, there's a dial on the side, make your selection,

Light or dark, crispy or brown,

If it pops too soon, push it back down. Make TOAST yeah TOAST!
